Dreams really do come true ♥️🎄🗽10 pics can't possibly encapsulate how magical this weekend was, but here's my attempt. Truly spoiled by you @nickalitus_ .... thank you for making this the most memorable and amazing birthday yet 🥰 you made every minute so fun. I love you!!! 

(see my story highlight "NYC" for more behind the scenes, and I just had to add the Live Photo sound from our tour guide at the end of this feed hahahaha)

Biggest shock of the century....... I'm still speechless !!!!! Can't wrap my head around this but all I can say is God is GOOD and He is FAITHFUL and I'm about to be Mrs. Andrews forever !!!!!!!! I love you @nickalitus_ 🤍 🤍 🤍

When I was 22 I went to a prayer night for women and I asked God to tell me about my future husband. As I waited and listened for His prompt, the number "26" came to my head and that's all I heard or saw.

Not knowing exactly what that meant, I took it that I would meet my husband when I was 26.

22 year old me hadn't even scratched the surface on mastering patience-- so I begged God that it would be sooner than that. 😅

Well..... the years came and went and I saw 26..... and by my 27th birthday I was confused. "Guess that wasn't what He meant" or "Maybe I didn't hear God" .... I tried to explain it away.

Little did I know, I had met my future husband at age 26. We were just coworkers and friends-- so it was no where on our radar that we'd even be romantically connected to each other.

Last year, I had an inkling that I was going to start dating my future husband (that's a whole 'nother conversation that I'd love to sit down and have coffee with you to tell 🥰)..... and when Nick and I decided that we would take our coworkers-turned friends-turned "I have feelings for you" relationship to the next level..... I realized.....

I met Nick when I was 26. 😳

I started dating him when I was 28. But here's the kicker.....

Because I have the honor and privledge of being a COUGAR (🐆🤪 rawr)..... Nick started dating ME when HE was 26!

Only God!

There have been so many other signs and inklings and words spoken that have lead us to this moment. But I can only pray that my season of waiting.... praying..... hoping.... hurting.... would not be in vain. God is good and God is faithful all the time. He's better than your doubts and fears and feelings of left-behindness.

Thank you God for this union and thank You for staying true to Your promises! Thank you for the blessing to my life that is Nick Andrews ♥️ @nickalitus_

I love you bubby tuna!!!!!

a dream come true..... 🤍✨ my very own bachelorette trip 😭

I've imagined this weekend for years knowing exactly who would be in attendance.... and I couldn't have imagined it to be as incredible as it was. I'm truly obsessed with every single lady who made this weekend beyond any experience I could ask and pray for. Thank you JESUS for every friendship and thank You for the best Bach trip ever 🪩🕺🏼👰🏼‍♀️ next up..... I'll be Mrs. Andrews!!!!!
